@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rhstth(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((0.13 / v1) / ((tmp + 0.20 / v0 + 0.14) + (v0 + 0.15 * v0 + 0.61)))
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.sin(v2 + 0.67) + (v2 + 0.01 * v0 + 0.76)))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.exp(v1 + 0.07)))
    data[tid] = v0
